# Language implementations live in separate repos with their own .gitignore.

# === Compat orchestration may clone impl repos locally under /compat/_work/ ===
compat/_work/

# === IDE ===
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

